    <item>
      <title>无论谁入主白宫，韩国都认为美国站在自己一边</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/south-korea-sees-us-by-its-side-regardless-of-who-is-in-white-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔一位高级官员称，韩国政府并不担心哪位候选人赢得美国总统大选，因为无论谁入主白宫，韩国政府都希望与他合作，共同应对朝鲜的核威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/south-korea-sees-us-by-its-side-regardless-of-who-is-in-white-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 22:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席执行官在法国被拘留后，Telegram 表示其遵守欧盟法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/telegram-says-it-abides-by-eu-laws-after-ceo-detained-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，Telegram 对法国拘留首席执行官帕维尔·杜罗夫 (Pavel Durov) 的理由提出质疑，杜罗夫是该通讯应用程序的亿万富翁联合创始人，上周末在巴黎机场被拘留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/telegram-says-it-abides-by-eu-laws-after-ceo-detained-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 21:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳副总统表示将签署反 LGBTQ 法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/ghana-vice-president-says-he-d-sign-anti-lgbtq-bill-into-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果加纳副总统马哈穆杜·巴武米亚 (Mahamudu Bawumia) 在 12 月的总统选举中获胜，他将颁布一项法案，要求对认定为 LGBTQ 的人判处三年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/ghana-vice-president-says-he-d-sign-anti-lgbtq-bill-into-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 21:34:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国电动汽车制造商对欧盟的冷淡回应在关税争端中付出了高昂代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/china-ev-maker-s-tepid-reply-to-eu-proves-costly-in-tariff-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上汽集团受到欧盟谈判代表的严厉对待，正成为一个警示，表明中国企业不具备在西方商业和政治领域开展业务的条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/china-ev-maker-s-tepid-reply-to-eu-proves-costly-in-tariff-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西山火肆虐 当局启动纵火调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/brazilian-authorities-launch-arson-probes-as-wildfires-rage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[环境部长玛丽娜·席尔瓦表示，巴西各地的山林火灾是由于低湿度和热浪引起的，但也有犯罪活动造成的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/brazilian-authorities-launch-arson-probes-as-wildfires-rage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 19:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
