    <item>
      <title>加拿大释放公共土地解决住房短缺问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/canada-frees-up-public-lands-to-tackle-housing-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府确定了 56 处联邦地产，面积相当于约 2,000 个冰球场，可在这些地产上建造数百套新的经济适用房，以应对可用土地稀缺导致的住房短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/canada-frees-up-public-lands-to-tackle-housing-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 17:04:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列轰炸黎巴嫩阻止袭击 中东局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/mideast-on-edge-after-israel-bombs-lebanon-to-thwart-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一百架以色列战机飞越黎巴嫩南部，以所谓的先发制人的打击摧毁了真主党数千个导弹发射器，几个小时后，中东地区准备迎接一场可能涉及伊朗及其盟友民兵的扩大战火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/mideast-on-edge-after-israel-bombs-lebanon-to-thwart-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 16:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京会见指挥官，泽连斯基谈及“公平和平”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-wants-kursk-incursion-to-nudge-russia-toward-peace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，乌克兰在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区的行动是更广泛的军事、政治和外交努力的一部分，旨在让俄罗斯接受“公平的和平”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-wants-kursk-incursion-to-nudge-russia-toward-peace</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 12:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称对黎巴嫩真主党发动了更多空袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-25/urgent-israel-says-it-is-staging-airstrikes-inside-lebanon-targeting-the-shiite-militia-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耶路撒冷（美联社）——周日凌晨，以色列和黎巴嫩激进组织真主党发生了激烈交火，但双方均未引发人们普遍担心的全面战争，双方都表示数月来最激烈的交火已经结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-25/urgent-israel-says-it-is-staging-airstrikes-inside-lebanon-targeting-the-shiite-militia-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 02:23:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
